OL,3,CHow man-made snow is ensuring a future
OL,4,Cfor Scotland's ski resorts
OL,6,FScotland's ski resorts are relying on
OL,7,Finnovative ways to create their own
OL,8,Fsnow as climate change threatens the
OL,9,Fsnow sports industry. STV News
OL,10,FReporter Vanessa Taaffe explains.
OL,12,FWords by ITV News Producer Stephanie
OL,13,FDocherty
OL,15,FFor decades, the highlands have been
OL,16,Fthe heart of Scotland's winter sports
OL,17,Findustry.
