OL,3,CHow man-made snow is ensuring a future
OL,4,Cfor Scotland's ski resorts
OL,6,FOnce being able to guarantee snowy
OL,7,Flandscapes from autumn right through
OL,8,Fto spring, these hills were a winter
OL,9,Fwonderland for skiing and snowboarding
OL,10,Fenthusiasts.
OL,12,FBut of late, that promise has been
OL,13,Fgetting harder to keep thanks to the
OL,14,Fchanging climate.
