OL,3,CHow man-made snow is ensuring a future
OL,4,Cfor Scotland's ski resorts
OL,6,FFor the many resorts and ski centres
OL,7,Fthat rely on the snow, these last few
OL,8,Fyears have been difficult, persuading
OL,9,Fsome to take matters into their own
OL,10,Fhands.
OL,12,FGlencoe Mountain Resort is one that
OL,13,Fhas invested in technology to create
OL,14,Fits own snow in order to get through
OL,15,Fthe season.
OL,17,FThe resort uses technology, called the
OL,18,FSnow Factory, to supplement natural
OL,19,Fsnowfall and ensure snow cover for
OL,20,Fskiing and sledging, especially during
OL,21,Fwarmer or drier spells.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
