OL,3,CHow man-made snow is ensuring a future
OL,4,Cfor Scotland's ski resorts
OL,6,FThis machine produces 100 cubic meters
OL,7,Fdaily to keep slopes open for longer
OL,8,Fand is crucial for the industry.
OL,10,FCharlie Munro works at the resort. He
OL,11,Fsays this technology has kept them in
OL,12,Fbusiness as they have been able to
OL,13,Fdepend less and less on natural
OL,14,Fsnowfall.
OL,16,F"The last couple of years haven't been
OL,17,Fvery good, so we have been relying on
OL,18,Fthe Snow factory to get going. This
OL,19,Fweekend we're open for sledging, so
OL,20,Fwe'll push it (the snow) out on Friday
OL,21,Fnight," he said.
