OL,3,CHow man-made snow is ensuring a future
OL,4,Cfor Scotland's ski resorts
OL,6,F"We don't want it, but it's a
OL,7,Fnecessity for the business to keep
OL,8,Fmoving forward. We hope mother nature
OL,9,Fhelps us as well, but unfortunately,
OL,10,Fsometimes it doesn't."
OL,12,FIt takes 2,000 litres of water a day
OL,13,Fto produce their snow, and it needs to
OL,14,Fbe kept at 25C.
OL,16,FResort owner, Andy Meldrum, says all
OL,17,Fthis effort and investment is worth it
OL,18,Ffor the long-term future of the snow
OL,19,Fsports industry in Scotland.
