OL,3,CHow man-made snow is ensuring a future
OL,4,Cfor Scotland's ski resorts
OL,6,FHe said: "The difference between a
OL,7,Fgood and a bad season here can
OL,8,Fsometimes be a weather front moving 10
OL,9,Fmiles too far north.
OL,11,F"Last year we only had 10,000 people
OL,12,Fup skiing, but we had over 30,000
OL,13,Fpeople come up to go sledging, and we
OL,14,Fcan do that with our advanced snow
OL,15,Fmaking system, a small 100 metre long
OL,16,Fslope and a magic carpet."
