OL,3,CHow man-made snow is ensuring a future
OL,4,Cfor Scotland's ski resorts
OL,6,FEarlier this year, the chief executive
OL,7,Fof the Cairngorm Mountain resort told
OL,8,Fthe Scottish Parliament the industry's
OL,9,Fbusiness model must move away from
OL,10,Freliance on snow and make sure there
OL,11,Fare activities all year-round if the
OL,12,Fbusinesses are to survive.
OL,14,FMike Gifford discussed the need to
OL,15,Foffer activities which do not rely on
OL,16,Fsnow when he appeared before the
OL,17,FPublic Audit Committee at the Scottish
OL,18,FParliament in September.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
