OL,3,CHow man-made snow is ensuring a future
OL,4,Cfor Scotland's ski resorts
OL,6,FHe said the business model had become
OL,7,Ftoo snow-dependent, which has
OL,8,Fcontributed to losses.
OL,10,F"I've been in the ski industry for
OL,11,Fabout 25 to 30 years now," he told the
OL,12,FMSPs.
OL,14,F"Going forward, we need to diversify.
OL,15,FWe've done the slope for mountain
OL,16,Fbiking and adventure play areas, and
OL,17,Fwe've put in a campervan parking area.
OL,19,F"What I want to do going forward is to
OL,20,Fenhance all of those and make sure
OL,21,Fthey're all running well.
